NOTE: This is SYNTHETIC (simulated) well-log data generated for testing /
modelling purposes. It approximates typical West-Siberian (Khanty-Mansiysk
region) stratigraphy and petrophysical trends (Quaternary-Neogene cover,
Pokur/Kuznetsovsk/Berezovsk/Gankinsk formations, Vikulovo-Alym reservoirs,
Achimov strata, Bazhenov source-rock shale, Vasyugan/Tyumen Jurassic
reservoirs, pre-Jurassic basement) but does NOT represent measurements from
a real well.
